  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Enjoy a varied continental buffet breakfast each morning with cereals, toast, honey, jams and plenty of other options. Six days of your stay you will also be treated to hot options from the buffet. </p>
<p>Afternoon tea and coffee with cake is complimentary and served in the lounge area six days of the week. You will also be able to purchase drinks from the bar during this time. </p>
<p>Dinner is a four course buffet served six days of the week including salad/antipasta/starters plus pasta and main courses and then cheese and desserts.</p>
<p>There is also a pre-dinner glass of prosecco and a choice of red, white or rose wines with dinner followed by tea &amp; coffee.</p>
<p>There's a special celebration menu on Christmas Day and New Year's Eve.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
