  <description><![CDATA[<p>Ideally located next to the main Crest gondola, the Hotel de Champoluc offers doorstep skiing and a warm welcome from the team. A brand new wellness area for this Winter is the perfect place to relax after a day on the slopes.</p>
<h2>Doorstep skiing</h2>
<p>Hotel de Champoluc offers ultimate convenience for getting on the slopes easily and without any fuss. The Crest gondola is just outside and at the end of the day, a piste will bring you back to the hotel. It is classified as a black run, but its lovely long and cruisy stretches can happily be skied by skiers with a few weeks experience. There are blue runs leading to the mid-station so beginner skiers can then take the gondola down the last stretch.</p>
<h2>Welcoming team</h2>
<p>The hotel is run by owner Max and his team who can't wait to welcome you for your Inghams trip to <a data-udi="umb://document/090d2ea7dadc4d03ba25ba2f7aaac686" href="/{localLink:umb://document/090d2ea7dadc4d03ba25ba2f7aaac686}" title="Champoluc">Champoluc</a>. There's a real sense of authenticity thanks to the Italian team so you really feel like you're on holiday.</p>
<p>Our Inghams Rep will take care of all your skiing needs, sharing the best runs, après and more to ensure you have a fabulous time.</p>
<p>The hotel's wellness area is the perfect spot to chill out. With a sauna, steam room, sensory shower, relaxation room and infrared chairs there is nowhere better to rest your ski legs. The spa is free of charge but a time slot must be booked locally.</p>
<h2>Traditional Italian hotel</h2>
<p>There's a really nice feeling to this hotel, with traditional Alpine wood features welcoming you in. The bar and dining rooms are a great setting for afternoon tea and chilling out, followed by a lovely evening meal.</p>
<h3>Why is this an Inghams' Choice property?</h3>
<p><strong>Service</strong><span></span>- We value the great partnerships we have with our hotels and our longstanding relationship with the Hotel De Champoluc means we know you are getting the very best on your Inghams holiday.</p>
<p><strong>Location </strong>- Make the most of your time in the Aosta Valley with doorstep skiing and easy access to the lifts.</p>
<p><strong>Value for money</strong>- Large bedrooms and easy slope access make the Hotel De Champoluc excellent value for money. House wine is included with dinner so you can try some great Italian wines too.</p>]]></description>
