  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>Attractive dining room, residents bar and lounge area</li>
<li>Billiard and darts room</li>
<li>Wellness area with sauna, steam room, sensory shower, relaxation area and infrared chairs, book locally - 15+ years </li>
<li>Massage and beauty treatment are payable locally</li>
<li>Heated ski &amp; boot storage</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Ski room</li>
</ul>
<p>The Monterosa Wellness Centre is a fantastic place to spend an afternoon and guests staying at Hotel de Champoluc receive a discounted entry rate. Speak to the hotel reception team locally to make a booking. Discounted rate is €30 on a weekday and €40 on the weekend which allows you 4 hours to enjoy the facilities. Just remember to pack your swimwear as these, slippers and robes are not included in the cost. </p>
<p><strong>Family Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Children's playroom (unsupervised)</li>
<li>Family rooms</li>
</ul>
<h2>Family discount offers</h2>
<p>Book your next family ski holiday for winter 2024/25 and enjoy discounts when booking this family friendly hotel:</p>
<p><img style="width: 728px; height: 313px;" src="/media/13105090/discount-child-places-838.jpg?width=728&amp;height=313&amp;mode=max" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/ee7f5ed172be4092ab5d33b79e1ca7ff" /></p>
<p>For more information on family ski holidays, and these discounts, please click <a data-udi="umb://document/a543e1407c404a978d9b4539252fc875" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a543e1407c404a978d9b4539252fc875}" title="Family Ski Holidays">here</a>.</p>]]></facilityDescription>
